<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/425408-could-simon-be-the-father-of-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Could Simon be the father of the Twin?<br /><br />Twin's mother used to work as a cleaning lady at the police station. At the end of the book, Else says to Kari about Simon that "..he must have an an illegitimate child somewhere.." The following paragraph reads: "Kari nodded. She had remembered the little old lady who cleaned at the police station and whose name had eventually come back to her." <br /><br />What do you think? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
